quest.name: Lominsan Rubbish
journal: Osment at Crescent Cove is vexed by litter in the area.
A merchant from Limsa Lominsa has left rubbish scattered about the docks. Clean it up as a service to the distressed Osment.
You have finished cleaning up the rubbish that littered the docks. Speak to Osment once more.
Though cleanliness has been restored, Osment is already lamenting the next Lominsan sloth who will darken his docks.
objectives: Clean up the rubbish on the docks.

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Ugggh, what a pain in the bloody arse. Who do those Lominsans think they are, anyway?

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Just look at all this, would you? A merchant from Limsa Lominsa dumped this junk when he shipped out. Claimed it wasn't fit for sellin', so he just up and left it!

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Barbarians! What passes for etiquette across the Strait of Merlthor?

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Don't suppose I could ask you to clean up the rest for me, eh? Please? I've picked up so much junk already, the mere sight of it fair makes me gag.

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Thank you, friend. Seeing this place clean again does my spirit good.

dialogue.name: OSMENT
dialogue.text: Though, I suppose some other Lominsan merchant will be by before long and leave more filth behind. <sigh> I hate my life.
